Oh. my.

7
00:00:18.086 --> 00:00:20.988
Something brought me
from the dirt today.

8
00:00:21.089 --> 00:00:22.440
A presence most evil.

9
00:00:22.523 --> 00:00:24.024
Although you know
me as a hardworking

10
00:00:24.125 --> 00:00:26.927
publicist. I am. in
fact. Elias Woodstone.

11
00:00:27.027 --> 00:00:28.562
