Oh. actually. DEFCON 1
is the most dangerous.

36
00:01:24.452 --> 00:01:25.453
Not now. Pete.

37
00:01:25.586 --> 00:01:26.671
Sam.

38
00:01:26.754 --> 00:01:29.006
did the bubble wrap
I ordered arrive?

39
00:01:30.424 --> 00:01:31.842
I'm gonna need you
to wrap me up. babe.

40
