Why are you tapping your toe?

76
00:02:42.230 --> 00:02:43.464
It's just a nervous tic.

77
00:02:44.298 --> 00:02:45.783
We're all nervous. Jay.

78
00:02:45.866 --> 00:02:47.301
Thank you. guys.

79
00:02:48.902 --> 00:02:51.372
-Hey!
-Yee-hah!

80
00:02:59.213 --> 00:03:00.548
