86
00:03:09.490 --> 00:03:12.693
Thor never skip day.
Thor very ambidextrous.

87
00:03:12.793 --> 00:03:13.944
He doesn't always nail it.

88
00:03:14.027 --> 00:03:15.728
Jay. I was thinking.
maybe we should

89
00:03:15.829 --> 00:03:17.348
