125
00:04:19.927 --> 00:04:21.329
this seems like a terrible plan.

126
00:04:21.428 --> 00:04:23.163
Well. it's the one to beat.

127
00:04:23.263 --> 00:04:25.633
Uh. Sam. Elias Woodstone is here

128
00:04:25.766 --> 00:04:27.285
