130
00:04:29.770 --> 00:04:31.021
Okay.

131
00:04:31.104 --> 00:04:33.874
Let's just hear
what he has to say.

132
00:04:34.742 --> 00:04:36.344
Wait. wait.

133
00:04:37.311 --> 00:04:38.779
