fled the property.

161
00:05:35.903 --> 00:05:38.271
Oh. boy. Yeah. I didn't
think about it that way.

162
00:05:38.372 --> 00:05:40.741
Although. I mean. with all
this Jay stuff going on.

163
00:05:40.841 --> 00:05:42.201
