172
00:06:01.695 --> 00:06:03.196
Can't blame a girl for trying.

173
00:06:03.296 --> 00:06:06.400
Is there anyone for
her in the basement?

174
00:06:06.500 --> 00:06:08.636
Creepy Dirk is newly single.

175
00:06:08.736 --> 00:06:10.571
