193
00:06:44.572 --> 00:06:46.607
Oh. damn. it's about to go down.

194
00:06:46.707 --> 00:06:48.993
She says she's gonna
smite him. Jay.

195
00:06:49.076 --> 00:06:50.778
Say goodbye. demon.

196
00:06:54.181 --> 00:06:55.282
What's happening?

197
00:06:55.415 --> 00:06:56.934
