199
00:06:58.952 --> 00:07:00.337
Not exactly.

200
00:07:00.420 --> 00:07:02.255
Smite! Smite! Smite!

201
00:07:02.389 --> 00:07:05.158
Smite! Smite!

202
00:07:05.258 --> 00:07:07.094
Smite!

203
00:07:07.227 --> 00:07:10.180
Is this your whole plan?
Just to yell "smite?"

204
00:07:10.263 --> 00:07:11.682
I mean. it does

205
00:07:11.765 --> 00:07:13.033
