206
00:07:13.133 --> 00:07:14.151
Patience. have you
ever done this before?

207
00:07:14.234 --> 00:07:15.435
Well. not exactly.

208
00:07:15.536 --> 00:07:18.038
but I just assumed on
account of my holiness

209
00:07:18.138 --> 00:07:20.140
