my end of the bargain.

226
00:07:51.038 --> 00:07:52.557
I mean. you made a
deal with the Devil.

227
00:07:52.640 --> 00:07:54.241
You should get
something in return.

228
00:07:54.341 --> 00:07:55.943
So. in exchange for Jay's soul.

229
00:07:56.043 --> 00:07:59.229
