restaurant on the map.

231
00:08:01.815 --> 00:08:04.652
So how long. exactly.
do I have left to live?

232
00:08:04.752 --> 00:08:06.103
Gosh. I mean.

233
00:08:06.186 --> 00:08:08.405
a rise from obscurity to
the top of the culinary heap

234
00:08:08.488 --> 00:08:09.690
