my end of the deal.

244
00:08:32.279 --> 00:08:34.481
Oh. one more thing...
it tapes tomorrow.

245
00:08:34.582 --> 00:08:36.049
After which you die.

246
00:08:36.149 --> 00:08:38.018
So. make it

247
00:08:38.118 --> 00:08:39.385
